We are moving! Been trying to really rest my heel for the past month and I finally put it to the test. Was shooting an ad a few days ago and thought this combo was pretty cool/unique. Still a little bit of pain in my heel after the session, but I’m pretty happy with how it held up! Going to stay away from tons of impact still. Freerunning with a bag is kinda funny 😅 

#parkour #freerunning #wallrun #doubleleg #heel #recovery #session #tmpst #tempestfreerunning #cava #flip #flips #tictac #jump #rock #nature #movement

Didn’t get to train as much as I would have liked at the Adrenaline Experience. Stayed pretty busy working on shit for the event and running around Vegas at night so I was pretty beat. Glad to get a quick line in with @corydemeyers right as we were tearing down the course and the webster trapdoor that was too obvious with this setup! 

Overall it was a great time and the KOTC2 qualifier went well. Hopefully we can pack it out next time ❤️‍🔥 thanks for having us @adrenalineworldwide ✌🏼
